| Plecotus | FM abrupt | 20-40 | [Brown long-eared bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/60518) (_Plecotus auritus_), [Grey long-eared bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/60527) (_Plecotus austriacus_), [Alpine long-eared bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/163463) (_Plecotus macrobullaris_) |
| Eptesicus | FM abrupt | 20-40 | [Serotine bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/60360) (_Eptesicus serotinus_), [Bicolored bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/60537) (_Vespertilio murinus_), [Natterer's bat](https://inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom/79302) (_Eptesicus nilssonii_) |

