## socio
- social
- social calls
- C1
- D1
- C2
- D2

* Social calls are more or less complex interaction sounds that require specific learning.
* A thesis by German Guido Pfalzer has allowed for the creation of a first compilation for European species; [its English translation by Yann Galger is available here](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1aBBtsV2ezhd907e-sEGQm5Zj2L2OD0pL/view).
* In France, [a compilation was produced by Olivier Vinet in 2023](https://www.vigienature.fr/sites/vigienature/files/documents/baseref_chiros-cs_vinet-bas_v1.pdf).
* This [dedicated search engine](https://cse.forge.apps.education.fr//#https://github.com/guillaumarchais/SearX/blob/main/chirossons) can also help you find examples of sounds visible on spectrograms. (Click on the image search once on the results page. Entering scientific names will yield more examples from English-language sources).

